msgstr "ເຊີເວີເມລ"

#. module: google_gmail
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/google_gmail/models/google_gmail_mixin.py:0
msgid "Only the administrator can link a Gmail mail server."
msgstr "ມີພຽງຜູ້ດູແລລະບົບເທົ່ານັ້ນທີ່ສາມາດເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ເຊີເວີເມລ Gmail ໄດ້."

#. module: google_gmail
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/google_gmail/models/google_gmail_mixin.py:0
msgid "Oops, we could not authenticate you. Please try again later."
msgstr "ຂໍອະໄພ, ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ສາມາດຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງທ່ານໄດ້. ກະລຸນາລອງໃໝ່ໃນພາຍຫຼັງ."

#. module: google_gmail
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/google_gmail/controllers/main.py:0
msgid ""
"Oops, you're creating an authorization to send from %(email_login)s but your"
" address is %(email_server)s. Make sure your addresses match!"
msgstr ""
"ຂໍອະໄພ, ທ່ານກຳລັງສ້າງການອະນຸຍາດເພື່ອສົ່ງຈາກ %(email_login)s ແຕ່ທີ່ຢູ່ຂອງທ່ານແມ່ນ %"
"(email_server)s. ກະລຸນາກວດສອບໃຫ້ແນ່ໃຈວ່າທີ່ຢູ່ອີເມລນັ້ນກົງກັນ!"

#. module: google_gmail
